volume.name: Giles: Sunday Express and Daily Express Cartoons

description:
Get ready for the ULTIMATE homage to 80's action movies!! Heavy Weapon will blow you away you with more bullets, one-liners, and 80's movie nods than you can shake a grenade at!

For nearly a decade, Sergeant John Magnum was part of an elite Special Forces group. After his entire battalion was massacred in front of him during the Vietnam War, he became consumed with guilt and decided to leave the military for good. He just wanted to live a normal life and forget his violent past...

...But now, years later, Magnum learns that his mentor, Colonel Deckard, was captured during a failed mission to South America and is being tortured at the hands of his ruthless captors. Angered at the thought of losing another one of his men, Magnum vows that to exact his revenge on everyone in his path to save him!
name: GN

description:
a JIMMY DYDO adventure

Trapped and abandoned on a strange world,

Jimmy Dydo searches for truth of his past, his presence, and how he came to be.

Jimmy befriends a baby Dragon along the way who helps in his search. He wonders...Was he created in a lab? ...Perhaps by a machine?...Was he part of an experiment? Maybe he's from another planet? His origin will be told one day... But, not until he makes sense of this new strange land...
